John Deere Heaven, Part 1
















Item Number: JDHEAVEN1


 Review Average:  
 Number of Reviews: 1

 View Reviews | Review this item


												        
							   	    Unit Price: $9.99
							

In Stock






Quantity 
								









Bookmark This Page
Refer this page to a friend























 Detailed Description

			           	           
						Welcome to John Deere Heaven � where all is mellow and even the cows are green and yellow. We first visited John Deere Heaven in All About John Deere Part 4, and people enjoyed the trip so much we decided to return and stay for an entire show.
 
See John Deere toys come alive in this fanciful, fast-paced mix of toy trains, tractors, and big machines. TM�s video magic will thrill and delight young and old alike. See O gauge and Standard gauge John Deere trains zip around elaborately detailed train layouts along with John Deere 1/16th, 1/50th and 1/64th scale tractors, cars, and trucks. Plus ten original songs by our favorite singer/songwriter James Coffey. Otto is in town and his little switch engine is blocking the mainline and  here comes the Circus Train! Oh no! 

If you love John Deere toys, music, and fun�buy this    
DVD. You�ll love it. 
Guaranteed.
45 minutes

Customer Reviews
"John Deere Heaven Part 1 is a DVD in which stop-motion animation makes beloved John Deere toys come alive. Ten original songs by singer and songwriter James Coffey spice up the elaborate miniature train layouts and interactions between exquisitely accurate replicas of machines. Young and old toy collectors alike are sure to enjoy watching 1/16, 1/50, and 1/64 scale tractors, cars, and trucks vroom about in this entertaining show, especially recommended for tractor lovers."
 Midwest Book Review

"The children really love this video if they love John Deere tractors. It also shows trains so it covers two areas boys adore."
Sarah Gerber








