The Infinite Wisdom of Love






USD 40.00
Featuring Dr. John Demartini
1 x DVD










 













Exploring and expanding your awareness and potential


 


In this incredible DVD, Dr.
John Demartini shares insights, knowledge and practical tools which will expand
your awareness and potential in all areas of your life. The program is a mix of
excerpts of Dr Demartini on stage and correlating interview extracts which
addresses values, goal setting, purpose and how to dissolve whatever is
blocking your true potential. Be prepared to open your eyes to a new
perspective where thoughts, love and gratitude have the power to shape your
reality.
 


  
		  
		  
	




